Subject: [PATCH 1/1] esys-utils standalone install

---
 factory/templates/meson.build  |  2 ++
 meson.build                    | 21 +++++++++++++++++++--
 meson_options.txt              |  2 ++
 src/bless-boot/meson.build     | 10 +++++++---
